                ‡¶ú‡¶∞‡ßÅ‡¶∞‡¶ø ‡¶°‡ßá‡¶≤‡¶ø‡¶≠‡¶æ‡¶∞‡¶ø (+‡ß´‡ß¶ ‡¶ü‡¶æ‡¶ï‡¶æ) - ‡ß®‡ß™ ‡¶ò‡¶®‡ßç‡¶ü‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶Æ‡¶ß‡ßç‡¶Ø‡ßá
              </Label>
            </div>

            {orderData.paymentMethod !== 'cod' && (
              <div className="flex items-center space-x-2">
                <input
                  type="checkbox"
